PrecisAmendments to the ATLANTIC FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1985 which expand the silver hake fishery to areas beyond the Scotian Shelf due to the invention of an otter trawl fitted with a specially-designed grate, and redraw the boundary line between Lobster Fishing Areas 33 and 34 so that it reflects traditional fishing patterns.
